    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Deduce Together&quot; is a cooperative and competitive online multiplayer game where players ask the AI about characters, locations, and more to uncover the correct answers.<br>Try asking questions that can be answered with &quot;YES&quot; or &quot;NO&quot; to the given problems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Private Session:</strong> Only players who know the room information can join. Enjoy the game privately with friends or acquaintances.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Competitive Gameplay:</strong> Players compete against each other to achieve the highest accuracy rate. Deduction and questioning skills are key.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable Game Settings:</strong> Adjust the challenge level by freely setting time limits and the number of questions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge your reasoning skills and aim to become the ultimate knowledge champion in dedicated sessions with friends and acquaintances!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently, you can use the default question set and user-created question sets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>default question set</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character Quiz (Beginner)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >World Tourist Spot Quiz (Beginner)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Historical Figure Quiz (Beginner)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Country Quiz</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movie Quiz (Beginner)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Quiz (Beginner)</p></li></ul>",
